Arnold does a good job teaching 347. He definitely goes faster than he should, but you learn a lot. It's a very interesting course with a lot of fun material, and he's the only prof that teaches it at UTM. I highly recommend this class, even if you're not in information security. It really opens you to a branch of cs you'd otherwise skip.
